---


 const personalImageAlt = "Andres Villarreal"
---

<article class="grid items-center gap-10 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 md:grid-cols-2">

  <!-- TEXT -->
  <div class="space-y-6">
    
    <!-- Tagline -->
    <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-100">
      🚀 I build scalable systems that solve real-world problems.
    </p>

    <!-- Description -->
    <div class="[&>p]:mb-4 [&>p>strong]:text-yellow-500 dark:[&>p>strong]:text-yellow-100 [&>p>strong]:font-normal [&>p>strong]:font-mono text-pretty">
      <p>
        Software developer specializing in <strong>.NET</strong> and backend systems, with experience building scalable APIs, cloud solutions, and modern web applications.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently working as an Electronic Technician, combining software knowledge with <strong>hands-on hardware expertise—deploying Linux systems</strong> and optimizing rugged devices for real-world performance.
      </p>
      <p>
        I bring a balanced skill set across frontend and backend, working with SQL, modern frameworks, and clean architectures. I also build data workflows, applying ETL processes with <strong>Python</strong> and <strong>Pandas</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Tech Stack -->
    <div>
      <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400">⚙️ Tech Stack</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs">
        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10">.NET Core</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10">AWS</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10">Docker</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10">Kubernetes</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10">SQL</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10">PostgreSQL</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10">JavaScript</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10">Angular</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10">Astro</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Strengths -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
      <div>🚀 Backend & APIs</div>
      <div>☁️ Cloud & DevOps</div>
      <div>📊 Data & ETL</div>
      <div>🛠 Hardware & Linux</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Current Focus -->
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
      🎯 Currently focused on backend scalability, cloud architecture, and performance optimization.
    </p>

  </div>

  <!-- IMAGE -->
  <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-end">
    <div class="relative w-64 group">
      <img 
        src="/me3.jpg" 
        alt={personalImageAlt} 
        class="object-cover w-64 aspect-square p-1 rotate-3 lg:p-2 rounded-2xl 
               bg-black/20 dark:bg-yellow-500/5 
               ring-1 ring-black/70 dark:ring-white/20 
               animate-flip-up
               transition-all duration-500
               group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:-translate-y-1 group-hover:rotate-0" 
        style="object-position: 50% 50%"
      />

      <!-- Badge -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full 
                  bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10
                  text-white
                  opacity-100 md:opacity-0 translate-y-0 md:translate-y-2
                  transition-all duration-500
                  md:group-hover:opacity-100 md:group-hover:translate-y-0">
        🚀 Open to Opportunities
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</article>